    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras/9503e5b9934e7d4c901afc08801d0fcc.avif?t=1731528228\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras_big/9503e5b9934e7d4c901afc08801d0fcc.avif?t=1731528228 width=800 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Draw according to the instructions</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras/9516271564719bf9c2d8120ec7ea4dd4.avif?t=1731528228\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras_big/9516271564719bf9c2d8120ec7ea4dd4.avif?t=1731528228 width=800 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Admire your creations</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras/a7724c7def101a6ea02f6c12b36057e0.avif?t=1731528228\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras_big/a7724c7def101a6ea02f6c12b36057e0.avif?t=1731528228 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try to guess as early as possible</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras/60b10009bb5dd79b5d9e552e92e823b2.avif?t=1731528228\" width=516 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delve into the complex relationship between a father and daughter</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras/882b76a47d9c056a3b5897c5815d48f1.avif?t=1731528228\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334050/extras_big/882b76a47d9c056a3b5897c5815d48f1.avif?t=1731528228 width=800 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the storyline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw with friends in multiplayer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create levels and share them with friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh at other players crooked drawings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our gaming community of great artists.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We're waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We hope that everything will work out for us :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support us on social networks, it is really important for us.</p>",
